race.comment: STAR INTRIGUE (2) is going well, winning comfortably here two back before a solid fourth at Coonamble over 1400m. Drops back to a winning trip with Gallagher sticking. Will press forward and take running down. EAST HARLEM (8) hit the line hard at Bathurst over this journey and looks ready to strike. Well placed and looms as a major threat. SAVETHEBESTTILLAST (4) improved third-up with a strong placing and backs up quickly. Still on the up and right in the mix.  MRS BULL (1) is a proven performer at this track and trip. Carries weight but gets the claim. Always competitive here.
